section.def:
animal
                (動物) means any form of animal life, whether alive
            or dead, or its part;

boating
                (船艇活動) means operating a vessel for pleasure,
            competition, recreation or tourism;

plant
                (植物) means a live or dead plant, or its
            part;

water-skiing
                (滑水) includes the skiing on water by aquaplane or
            other similar object, or the operating of a jet ski or water scooter;
